title: New Settings
itunes:title: New Settings
description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions

Edited by Diane Kang 

 

Kate finds herself in her new house in her new neighborhood while trying to not freak out about the commute to set. Leisha finds herself in a squeaky clean house in Texas thanks to some handy cowboys. Then they finally reveal some details for the new season of The L Word: Generation Q!
